<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<odoo>
  <!-- kisok.group tree view -->
  <record id="model_name_view_tree" model="ir.ui.view">
    <field name="name">kisok.group.view.tree</field>
    <field name="model">kisok.group</field>
    <field name="arch" type="xml">
      <tree>
        <field name="name" />
        <field name="product_id" />
        <field name="quantity" />
      </tree>
    </field>
  </record>

</odoo>
